This project demonstrates how to combine multiple datasets and retrieve related information using Excel's powerful lookup functions. Functions such as VLOOKUP, XLOOKUP, INDEX-MATCH, and XMATCH are used to merge data efficiently, eliminate redundancy, and create integrated datasets for business analysis. The project reflects real-world scenarios where information is retrieved across multiple tables.

Key Skills Demonstrated:
VLOOKUP
XLOOKUP
INDEX-MATCH
XMATCH
Data Merging
Data Retrieval
Relational Data Analysis
Advanced Excel Functions
